TAILWIND CSS CONVENTIONS
CLASS ORDER
Follow Prettier Tailwind plugin order: 
Layout (display, position, z-index) Box model (w, h, m, p) Typography (font, text, leading) Visual (bg, border, shadow, opacity) Interactive (hover, focus, active) Responsive (sm:, md:, lg:) 
NAMING CONVENTIONS
USE_SEMANTIC_CLASS_EXTRACTION_FOR_REPEATED_PATTERNS `@apply` in globals.css
DO NOT
NU \!important — fix specificity properly NU inline styles — always Tailwind or CSS modules Don't mix Tailwind with styled-components or emotion 
